arm_group.description:
Three treatments of different formulations of 50 mg BIBR 1048 MS (bid for 3 days) with 40 mg Pantoprazole (bid). Randomised sequence.
BIBR 1048 MS Capsule I with pantoprazole (bid for 3 days);
BIBR 1048 MS Capsule K with pantoprazole (bid for 3 days);
BIBR 1048 MS Drinking solution with Pantoprazole (bid for 3 days)

Three treatments of different formulations of 50 mg BIBR 1048 MS (bid for 3 days) without Pantoprazole. Fixed sequence.
BIBR 1048 MS Capsule K (bid for 3 days);
BIBR 1048 MS Drinking solution (bid for 3 days)
